7.1.3 Industry-Specific Solutions

· Autonomous Transportation: Integrated optimization, maintenance, and security
· Smart Grids: Grid resilience through hybrid intelligence
· Precision Agriculture: Resource optimization with security
· Healthcare 4.0: Patient-centric hybrid intelligent systems

7.2 Medium-Term (3-5 Years)

